WEBVTT

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:07.136
Shah Rukh Khan: Shelja Sen
from Delhi is a child psychologist.

00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:10.776
An expert on how to speak to children.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.776
The first time I heard of her,

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.337
I thought:

00:00:13.361 --> 00:00:16.736
if she needs to study the power of words,

00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:19.896
she should talk to my children.

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:24.616
It takes them a minute
to cut you down to size.

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:28.856
The two older ones,
who are now young adults,

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:31.536
are not interested in talking.